[node name="Level8" type="Node3D"]
editor_description = "Room 08 — Leaking Vials (greenhouse/chemical theme). Gear1 is a safe first hit with no timer. LeakingVial1/2/3 each destabilize on real elapsed time (not tied to Ball rewinds) and auto-detonate if left too long — an auto-detonation fires `leaked`, not `activated`, so it does NOT satisfy the win condition; LeakFailureHandler listens for that and reloads the room. GREYBOX FIRST PASS — destabilize_time per vial and room size are unverified numbers, expect to retune in-editor once someone's actually played it."

